 "html": "<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" class=\"size-medium wp-image-6242 aligncenter\" src=\"/media/uploads/2021/07/IMG_2076-2-225x300.jpg\" alt width=\"225\" height=\"300\" srcset=\"/media/uploads/2021/07/IMG_2076-2-225x300.jpg 225w, /media/uploads/2021/07/IMG_2076-2-600x800.jpg 600w, /media/uploads/2021/07/IMG_2076-2-768x1024.jpg 768w, /media/uploads/2021/07/IMG_2076-2-1152x1536.jpg 1152w, /media/uploads/2021/07/IMG_2076-2-750x1000.jpg 750w, /media/uploads/2021/07/IMG_2076-2-380x507.jpg 380w, /media/uploads/2021/07/IMG_2076-2-760x1013.jpg 760w, /media/uploads/2021/07/IMG_2076-2-800x1067.jpg 800w, /media/uploads/2021/07/IMG_2076-2.jpg 1536w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 225px) 100vw, 225px\"></p>\n<p><strong>OREO FUDGE</strong></p>\n<p><strong>BESTANDDELE</strong></p>\n<p>12 oreo koekies grof gebreek</p>\n<p>1 blikkie kondensmelk</p>\n<p>4 x 150g slabs witsjokolade</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><strong>METODE</strong></p>\n<ol>\n<li>Gooi die kondensmelk en sjokolade in ‘n bak wat in die mikrogolf kan gaan.Smelt die sjokolade vir so een minuut in die kondensmelk. Roer en maak seker die sjokolade smelt as jy dit inroer.</li>\n<li>Roer die grof gebreekte oreo koekies deur die mengsel</li>\n<li>Sit bakpapier onder in ‘n bak en krap jou mengsel daarin uit.</li>\n<li>Los dit in die yskas sodat dit kan stol.Haal uit en sny in blokke.</li>\n</ol>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" class=\"aligncenter wp-image-6242 size-large\" src=\"/media/uploads/2021/07/IMG_2076-2-768x1024.jpg\" alt width=\"530\" height=\"707\" srcset=\"/media/uploads/2021/07/IMG_2076-2-768x1024.jpg 768w, /media/uploads/2021/07/IMG_2076-2-600x800.jpg 600w, /media/uploads/2021/07/IMG_2076-2-225x300.jpg 225w, /media/uploads/2021/07/IMG_2076-2-1152x1536.jpg 1152w, /media/uploads/2021/07/IMG_2076-2-750x1000.jpg 750w, /media/uploads/2021/07/IMG_2076-2-380x507.jpg 380w, /media/uploads/2021/07/IMG_2076-2-760x1013.jpg 760w, /media/uploads/2021/07/IMG_2076-2-800x1067.jpg 800w, /media/uploads/2021/07/IMG_2076-2.jpg 1536w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 530px) 100vw, 530px\"></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>",
